      "content_html": "<p><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/hSPVuakrJqs\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1478265409131-1f65c88f965c?w=720\" alt=\"Photo by Kelly Sikkema\"></a></p>\n<p>Welcome! Here is the demo and documentation for Lume Theme Shiraha.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"../part-1-installation/\">Part 1: Installation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"../part-2-writing/\">Part 2: Writing</a></li>\n</ul>"
